        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverioDAI1"/>, p. 90, n. <citedRange>15</citedRange> (ph.)</bibl>,
                    whence <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.16</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>011900</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp.<citedRange>300-301</citedRange>, number 41, fragment a (text)</bibl>.</p>
            <p>For a general bibliography on the accounts of the damiergoi see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
