                                    <num value="1"><g type="cyrnum">–</g></num></measure></num></measure></num></supplied>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Dépenses, sacrifices de bovins inclus: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mines</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 21 drachmes 1 obole.
            Reste: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mines</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 28 drachmes 4 oboles.
            Indemnité pour les démiurges <supplied reason="lost">3 mines</supplied>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Expenses, sacrifices of oxen included: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mines</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 21 drachmas 1 obol.
            Remainder: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mines</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 28 drachmas 4 obols.
            Allowance for the damiergoi <supplied reason="lost">3 mines</supplied>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Uscite, sacrifici dei buoi inclusi: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mine</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 21 dracme 1 obolo.
            Resto: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mine</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 28 dracme 4 oboli.
            Retribuzione per i damiurghi <supplied reason="lost">3 mine</supplied>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>[---] النفقات متضمنة الأضحيات من الثيران: [---] [ميناي] [---]و21 دراخما و1 أوبول. الباقي: [---] [ميناي] [---]و28 دراخما و4 أوبول. ويُعطى للداميرجوي [3 ميناي].</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Oliverio provides a letter-height of 0.018, which seems too much; admitting that the stone's measures were right, we give our estimation for the letters.</p>
                <p>A large part of this inscription is restored with help of the parallel formulation of the other accounts.</p>
                <p>Additional commentary for <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr2"/></bibl>: <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/></bibl> offers a tantalizing joint of this fragment with 
                <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr013600</ref>. In favour of this view, he mentions a similar depth of the stones, approaching heights of the letters and a common use of a dotted omicron, this last point 
                    being not very clear at <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr013600</ref>. In fact, the preserved parts match well, adding to the present fragment the ends of its lines 3 to 5. Rosamilia 
                mentions a possible difference in the shape of the glyph <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ζ</foreign> for 50 mines: this does not seem convincing, as in both fragments we find an oblique 
                    drawing of this character. Conversely, there is a noticeable difference between the shape of the glyph <foreign xml:lang="grc"><g type="cyrnum">&gt;</g></foreign> (1 obol), which is 
                     here angular, whereas it has a lunate shape at <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr013600</ref>. For that reason, we do not follow Rosamilia in his reconstruction, the more so that the present 
                fragment was never seen again after Oliverio's publication.</p>
            </div></body>
